snippet.title: Birthday Mania for Atari 2600 Released! Gameplay Footage & Instructions
snippet.description:
**THIS VIDEO WILL NOT BE MONETIZED NOR DO I TAKE CREDIT. READ MY PINNED COMMENT, I UPDATED THE INSTRUCTIONS**

Please take the time to thank everyone at AtariAge for their hard work.

I apologize for another upload but and had to make this video on such short notice. I want to get this out there as fast as possible.

Source: https://atariage.com/forums/topic/204909-birthday-mania-unwrapped/page/11/#comments

Gameplay footage from Stella VCS Emulator using the mouse as the paddle controller.

Don't forget to like, comment & share!
